<h2 id="books">Books</h2>

<ol>
  <li><a href="https://leanpub.com/AroundTheWorldWith80SoftwareTesters">Around the world with 80 software testers</a> is a free book which draws upon the knowledge and experience from both experts and new voices from around the world involved in software testing. The book is free and currently available via LeanPub. The book is 27% complete with new contributions being added every other week.</li>
  <li><a href="https://twitter.com/AgileTD">Agile testing days</a> recently tweeted â€˜a great list of books every agile tester should readâ€™. Some of these books are free and the rest you can purchase either in physical or in an eFormat.</li>
</ol>
